<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Increased Launch Error Rates>
We are investigating increased error rates for new launches in the EU-CENTRAL-1 Region.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Service is operating normally: [RESOLVED] Increased Launch Error Rates>
Between 05:00 AM PDT and 05:37 AM PDT we experienced increased error rates for instance launches in the EU-CENTRAL-1 Region. Existing instances were unaffected. The issue has been resolved and the service is operating normally.
